data.description: This lovely home situated on a large lot in a cozy cul-de-sac. Remodeled kitchen has granite countertop with stainless steel appliances, refrigerator conveys to the buyers. The bathrooms have been remodeled with natural tone tiles and dark color cabinets. Beautiful shaded backyard. Laminate and tile throughout! The furnace replaced March 2014. The seller is replacing roof. Easy access to I-10 and 1604. Great location! Great floor plan. OPEN HOUSE: Aug. 27 & 28th 1:00-4:00
